I'm not having supper under broad daylight!

936
01:13:42,792 --> 01:13:46,125
系，个名叫晚餐啫，其实咪就係午餐？
What's in a name? It's the same as Lunch.

937
01:13:46,333 --> 01:13:49,750
好啦好啦，怕咗你啦！要两份晚餐啦！快啲手啊！
Great! Whatever you say! And make it quick!

938
01:13:49,917 --> 01:13:53,417
